Speaker 2: Yes, sir, I would like to—I have one refilled on my score blue.

Speaker 1: The RX number is—oh, your name and zip code can help me more.

Speaker 1: Okay, my—my address is one six five—

Speaker 2: Thanks.

Speaker 1: Okay, I—

Speaker 2: Got you. You said one six five zero zero eighty second Street, right?

Speaker 1: Yeah, one six five zero zero eighty second Street in Wisconsin.

Speaker 1: Okay. Thank you very much, sir. I appreciate it. You're welcome. We're set, Alfred. Have a good day.

Speaker 2: Okay, you too. Bye. Bye. Bye.
